Vodacom has revealed a range of deals on smartphone contracts and smartwatches for Black Friday 2019. The promotion includes a number of bundled smartphone contracts, with add-ons such as Samsung TVs, Bluetooth headsets, and more. The offers will be available from midnight on Friday 29 November until 2 December 2019, while stocks last. These deals are available exclusively at Vodacom World and on Vodacom’s online store. In addition to these smartphone and smartwatch deals, Vodacom is also expected to unveil more Black Friday deals closer to the sale period. Vodacom’s Black Friday 2019 smartphone and smartwatch offers can be found below. All smartphone deals listed below are 24-month contracts. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-330123 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-TV-and-Note-10-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-TV-and-Note-10.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-TV-and-Note-10-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Samsung-TV-and-Note-10-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />  <img class="aligncenter wp-image-330105 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/iPhone-7-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/iPhone-7.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/iPhone-7-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/iPhone-7-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-300602 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Huawei-Watch-GT-Active.jpg" alt="Huawei Wa